snippet.title: Remnants of Pentakill - Rock/stars (K/DA - Pop/stars Cover)
snippet.description:
Although K-pop started in Korea just like I was born here, maybe K-pop is the most distant genre of music I play. Why are the listeners of these two genres not coexisting together? 

However, as the League of Legends projects always try, I believe there will definitely be a connection somewhere in these two genres. So I took a new challenge with my friend, Friedrich. Did we really make the two genres a little closer? You can check it out here. Hope you Enjoy it!

Metal Christmas and Heavy New Year!
